Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再加上不想一直重复我是戴夫 奥斯本的\NPlus, I got tired of saying I was a super Dave Osborne
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.15,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-超级粉丝 -什么?!怎么会有人不想承认\N-fan. -What?! how could you get tired of telling people you're
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是他的超级粉丝?\Na super Dave Osborne fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我也该把它除掉了\N-Well, maybe I should get mine removed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-也许你该这么做 -我会的\N-Maybe you should. -Well, maybe I will.
