Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-很好 -我正试着清清除脑海里不停重复的\N-okay. -I'm just trying to clear something up in my head
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那句话 你是戴夫 奥斯本的超级粉丝吗?\Nas I go over it again.Are you a super Dave Osborne fan, or are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你只是不想再说你是他的超级粉丝?\Nyou tired of telling people you're a super Dave Osborne Fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你这有意思吗?\NWhy do you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-菜来了 请享用 -谢谢\N-There we go. Enjoy. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他这次有任何一道菜上对了吗?\NIs any of it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,至少装在盘子里这件事是对的\NIt's on a plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-我的挺不错啊 -彭 别为他找理由了\N-Well, mine looks fine. -Penn, stop defending him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你明明跟他说你对坚果过敏\NYou told him you're allergic to nuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,结果你的沙拉上全是核桃\Nand your salad's all pecan-crusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我可以吃旁边的这些...\NIt's okay.  I'm just gonna eat around it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我不能呼吸了\NOh, my God.   My throat's closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-我受够了 喂! -别这样 别这样\N-Okay. This has gotta stop. Hey! - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧 当服务生真的不容易\NOkay, look, please. It's really hard to be a waiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,算... -彭\NJust... -Penn,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要一些有建设性的批评意见\Nhe needs to hear some constructive criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白 但是...\NI know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以提高工作表现\Nit'll make him better at his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-他以后会感谢我的 服务员! -有事吗?\N-He'll thank me for it in the long run. Dude! -What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,兰迪 你以后得把菜单写下来了\NRandy, you gotta start writing stuff down, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没点派 彭妮差点呛死 -你说反了吧\N-I didn't order pie. Penny almost died. -Feel like you should be flipping those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是 他也总是把我点的弄错\NYeah, he always gets my order Wrong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,兰迪 又有人投诉你吗?\N-Randy, are you getting more complaints?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 只是我正在用的这种记忆法--\NNo, it's just, I have this mnemonic device that I'm using--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说过不能再被投诉了吗?\NI told you this can't happen again, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-出门左拐，因为你被解雇了 -什么?\N-Hit the road. You're fired. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你被解雇了!\NYou're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真是多谢你们了 所有这些...我都记住了\NOh, thanks a lot, man! Oh, and this... it's locked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但我...是你说...\NBut I... you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在谁都不认识我了?\NOh, so now y'all don't know nobody?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的?你们就这样对我?\NFor real? That's what's hot in the streets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你纹这个的时候什么情况?\NSo how hammered were you when you got this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,简单来说，一大把的头发都被我扯下来了\NLet's just say there was a lot of hair-holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-我要吐了 我又要吐了 -没事的 天啊\N-Hold my hair. Hold my hair. -Okay. I got it. Oh, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,加油!狗熊队\NGo, bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,加油!\NGo, bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,加油!狗熊队！哥呀\NGo, bears! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来挺悲催的\NSounds like a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们把这贱人名字弄掉吧\NWhat do you say we blast this bitch's name off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 你误会了\NOh. Whoa. No, no. It's--it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们还是好朋友 -哦 又是这种\N- We're actually still friends. - Oh. One of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-看样子你还余情未了啊 -不是的 只是-\N-Sounds like you have some unresolved feelings going on. -No, no. It's just that--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-啥时分的手啊? -四个月前吧\N-when did you break up? -About four months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-四个月前 恩 -不好意思\N-Four months ago. Uh-huh. -I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛把这些写下来? 跟这又没什么关--\NWhy are you writing that down? This has nothing to do with--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以我的经验来看 如果一段感情真的结束了\Nin my experience, if someone is truly over someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就会马上把纹身去掉\Nthey get those taken off right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,恩 你知道的 我真的很忙\NWell, I've been really busy, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,买V领T恤 穿V领T恤\Nbuying V-neck T-shirts, wearing V-neck T-shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这个真的占了我很多时间\NIt pretty much usurped most of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你要搞清楚两件事\NExactly. There are two things you need to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,第一 我不在乎你说的是真是假\NOne, I do not validate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,第二 在你消掉纹身之前\Nand two, you shouldn't get this done
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该把你窝着的感情先消掉\Nuntil you have all your feelings worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 消纹身是永久性的\NYou really need to understand, tattoo removal is permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦你把纹身去掉 就不能再纹上去了\NOnce you have a tattoo taken off, you cannot put it back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗，不是可以再重新--\NReally? 'cause I feel like I could just--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 嘘 嘘 好好想想我说的话\Nuh, shh, shh, shh. Just... think about what I said, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你不介意的话\NNow if you'll excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要帮一个女人去掉她脸上的五角星纹身\NI have to go remove a face pentagram
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,她参加了市政会竞选 我还投了她一票\Nfrom a woman who's running for city council. She's got my vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 三倍分区的二十分 我又赢了 克莱德\NBoom! Triple 20! I win again, Clyde!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不管你记不记得你投到哪里了\NI don't care that you don't remember where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 噢 别走 听到了吧?\NOh. Oh. Don't go anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哈啰?\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 是我 简\NHey, it's Jane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟那个英国小帅哥的约会怎么样了?\NHow's your date going with the brit boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 酷毙了 我知道艾德里安\NOh, it's awesome. I know, Adrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,切尔西 韩德勒 演得很假\NChelsea Handler has forgotten how to keep it real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们真的很来电\NWe're really hitting it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 太好了 嗯\NOh, I'm so glad to hear that. Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太棒了 -噢噢噢艾德里安刚走\NThat is just fantastic. -Ooh-Hoo-Hoo-hoo! Hey, you just missed Adrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么没在约会?\NWhy aren't you on your date?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯... 我不是很想去\NUh... look, I wasn't into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 我还要跟克莱德叙叙旧\NBesides, I needed to reconnect with Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是打电话取消约会了 还是放他鸽子了?\NSo did you at least call to cancel, or did you stand him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你放他鸽子了?\NYou stood him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 这没什么大不了的\NOh. It's not a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那你说他打电话问你在哪里\N-Well, what did you say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么说的?  -他根本没打电话\Nwhen he called to find out where you were? -He didn't call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么知道他没有放你鸽子?\NWell, then how do you know he didn't stand you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 你真心疯了\Nwhat? You're out of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 是不是你的魅力用完了 嗯?\NI mean, is it possible that Max got maxed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 第一 我很喜欢你把我的名字用作动词\NOkay, one, I love how you used my name as a verb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,要成为文化偶像的第一要素\NBig part of becoming a cultural icon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是我的目标\Nwhich you know is a goal of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,第二 闭上你的鸟嘴\NTwo, you shut your whore mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 踩到你痛处了?\NOoh. Touched a nerve?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没人比我更有魅力\NNo one maxes Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 拿上你的外套\NNow Let's go grab whatever wasp overcoat you wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去那家酒吧看看\NWe're gonna go down to that bar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那个瘦得像皮包骨的英国笨蛋\Nand see that he's sitting there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定还坐在那里 说着\Nlike a skinny, British Loser, all like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,(伦敦腔)"马科斯在哪里?\N(British accent) "Where's Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他没来 我的心都碎了" -你的衬衣穿反了\NHe broke my heart by Not showing up." -Your shirt inside out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对 我的衬衣是穿反了\Nyep. My shirt is inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-嗨 -嗨 我有点事情想问你\N-Hey. -Hey. I just wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好 进来吧 我正在泡茶\NYeah. Come on in. I was just making myself some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要喝点吗? -不 不用了\N-Do you want some? -No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我问你\NUm, let me ask you somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们分手了多久 你才把纹身去掉的?\NHow soon after the whole thing did you get your tattoo removed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我的纹身 问得好\NOh, my tattoo. Excellent question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我不记得了 大概一个星期吧\NUm, I don't know, like, a week or so. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 这么快\NYeah. That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 你的纹身也去掉了吗?\NYeah. Did you get yours taken off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,又是个自由的花花公子了?\NYou free to be a playa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.94,0:09:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-不要说"花花公子" -我一说完就后悔了\N-Don't say "playa." -I regretted it almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-有留疤吗? -嗯 有一点\N-So was there any scarring? -Yeah. A little. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意让我看一下吗 看看会是什么样子\NDo you mind if I took a look, just to see what I'm in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 我不愿意 -我不是说让你脱光什么的\N-Nah. I don't think so. -I-I wasn't trying to get you naked or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 我知道 我知道你不是那个意思\NNo, I know. I know that's not what you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-是啊 反正我们已经脱过几百次了\Nmeant. -Yeah, 'cause it-- it wouldn't be weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会觉得很奇怪  -是啊\Nbecause we've done it, like, a million times. -Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,大概脱了几百几千次了 是吧?\Nlike, a million bajillion times, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道该不该脱\NYeah. But I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-现在脱是很奇怪  -不 不奇怪\N-Now it's weird. -No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不 奇怪 -不奇怪\NNo, it is.  -It's not weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪 -是有点奇怪\NYeah. Ah, it's weird. -It's a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你会收到我发的\NLook, um, you're about to get
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一条特别长的道歉短信 别看了\Na really long apologize-y text from me. Don't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不得不发\NI just have to send it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你说艾德里安没有放我鸽子\NI'm telling you, Adrian did not stand me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是个稍微胖点的克里斯 奥唐纳\NI'm like a chubby Chris O'Donnell,
